        <updateDate>2003-12-22T19:42:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Directs the Broadcasting Board of Governors to conduct a pilot program for the promotion of travel and tourism in the United States through U.S. international broadcasting, particularly to regional economies that have been affected by the decrease in tourism following the events of September 11, 2001.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
